---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About · Evelyn Pottery" description="About Evelyn and her pottery practice.">
  <section class="page container">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p class="lead">Hi, I'm Evelyn — welcome to my little corner of clay.</p>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I make functional and decorative pottery from my home studio. Most pieces
        start on the wheel; others are hand-built by pinching, coiling, or slab work.
        Each one is glazed and fired individually, so no two ever come out quite the same.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is part gallery, part journal. The <a href="/blog">Journal</a> is
        where I write about what I'm working on, glaze experiments, kiln notes, and the
        occasional happy accident.
      </p>
      <p>
        Want to say hello or ask about a piece? Head to the
        <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
